overview: Maison Margiela presents the Artisanal Co-Ed Collection for Autumn-Winter 2020. Creative director John Galliano detects a desire for transparency: a new consciousness clarified by the illumination of the creative process and the human values it represents. Through the format of film, the Artisanal practice is captured by image-maker Nick Knight.
tagline: Maison Margiela Artisanal Co-Ed Collection Autumn-Winter 2020
title: S.W.A.L.K
